  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The LATINA registry aims at assessing a new classification of bifurcation restenosis in the
      prediction of major adverse cardiac events in patients who have previously undergone a
      succesful percutaneous bifurcation intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
